  %h4.mtop30 What is Cocopay?
  %p.mbottom30 Cocopay is the free payments and fundraising platform by users in India. On Cocociti you can share any wish of yours. Likewise, with the introduction of Cocopay; now anyone can raise funds for your personal causes like Travel, Health, Education or passion and creative wishes like Movies, Music, Theatre, Fashion, Technology or for NGOs, Non-Profits, Charities, causes from a large number of people who share passion for wishes like yours.

  %h4 Why Cocociti?
  %p.mbottom30 Cocociti is the world's simplest fundraising platform, loved by people. Using Cocociti for fundraising is as easy as using any other social network. Also, we have the most supportive social community and users to support the ecosystem
  Starting a fundraiser on Cocociti is FREE.
  There is no penalty if you don't raise the total amount. Whatever funds your raise will still get disbursed
  You can create and personalize your fundraiser page in minutes
  You get instant updates on your fundraiser's progress via email and SMS

  %h1 FAQs
  %h4 What is crowdfunding?
  %p.mbottom30 Crowdfunding is a process in which individuals pool money and other resources to fund projects initiated by other people or organizations. Crowdfunded projects may include creative works, products, nonprofit organizations, supporting entrepreneurship, businesses, or donations for a specific purpose (e.g., to pay for a medical procedure). Crowdfunding usually takes place via an online portal that handles the financial transactions involved, and may also provide services such as media hosting, social networking, and facilitating contact with contributors.

  %h4 What can I raise money for?
  %p.mbottom30 Anything ranging from raising funds for drinking tea, buying a fidget spinner, repairing your broken phone screen, funding your weekend trip and to paying unaffordable medical expenses, social causes . Users on Cocopay usually raise funds for:

