  %h4 Can I receive the raised amount in somebody else’s name?
  %p.mbottom30 In either of the above situations, the amount can be received by a family member or a friend, provided you submit your school or college ID along with the mandatory documents of the receiver.
  Please note: The amount shall be transferred only after the verification of documents.

  %h4 I am foreign national, can I still raise funds on Cocopay?
  %p.mbottom30 No, as of now only Indian citizens of age 18 and above can raise funds from Indian nationals.


  %h1 Miscellaneous

  %h4 Can I keep my fundraiser private?
  %p.mbottom30 All fundraisers on Cocopay are open to public viewing once they receive their first donation.

  %h4 Can we get any discount?
  %p.mbottom30 We are sorry. We are still a start up. We need to generate revenue too to keep you serving better. But as we go along, we look forward to reducing the charges.

  %h4 Is the money raised through Cocopay taxable?
  %p.mbottom30.pbottom100 You are liable to pay income tax or other taxes as er your local law. Please consult with a relevant tax expert for further details. If needed, the details of money raised for a particular wish will be disclosed to the concerned authorities.
